---
description: Phase gate rules
alwaysApply: true
---

- Complete current phase before starting next
- Run pnpm typecheck after each phase
- Run pnpm db:push after schema changes
- Member routes: @RequireSubscription() on backend
- Admin routes: @Roles(ADMIN, SUPER_ADMIN)
- Never commit .env files
- Razorpay dev mode when keys empty (auto-activate locally)
- Use docker compose up -d for local PostgreSQL
